    <!-- ============ QUALITY ============ -->
    <section class="mp-section" id="quality">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="mp-quality">
          <div class="mp-quality__main">
            <img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/jdpower-award.jpg" alt="J.D. Power award — GAC EMPOW R" />
          </div>
          <aside class="mp-quality__card">
            <div class="mp-quality__thumb"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/quality-thumb.jpg" alt="EMPOW R" loading="lazy" /></div>
            <div class="mp-quality__text">
              <span class="mp-quality__strapline">Extraordinary Standards</span>
              <p class="mp-quality__content">Winner of the J.D. Power prize for 8 Years in a row.</p>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ TECHNOLOGY ============ -->
    <section class="mp-section mp-section--grey" id="technology">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="mp-head mp-head--left">
          <h2 class="mp-head__title">Smart Technologies</h2>
          <p class="mp-head__sub">The ultimate driving experience with innovative technology</p>
        </header>
        <div class="mp-tech-banner"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/tech-banner.jpg" alt="EMPOW R smart technologies" /></div>
        <div class="mp-cards">
          <article class="mp-card">
            <div class="mp-card__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/tech-1.jpg" alt="Lane &amp; Traffic Jam Assist Technologies" /></div>
            <h3 class="mp-card__title">Lane &amp; Traffic Jam Assist Technologies</h3>
            <p class="mp-card__text">Stress-free traffic assistance.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="mp-card">
            <div class="mp-card__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/tech-2.jpg" alt="Passive Entry Passive Start system" /></div>
            <h3 class="mp-card__title">Passive Entry Passive Start (PEPS) System</h3>
            <p class="mp-card__text">Seamless vehicle access.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="mp-card">
            <div class="mp-card__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/tech-3.jpg" alt="Large digital instrument cluster and screens" /></div>
            <h3 class="mp-card__title">Large Digital Instrument Cluster and Screens</h3>
            <p class="mp-card__text">Your ride, reimagined: digital screens that make a statement.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ PERFORMANCE ============ -->
    <section class="mp-section" id="performance">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="mp-head mp-head--left">
          <h2 class="mp-head__title">Performance</h2>
          <p class="mp-head__sub">Seamless Control, Dynamic Force</p>
        </header>

        <div class="mp-tabs" data-tabs-wrap>
          <div class="mp-tabs__nav" data-tabs>
            <button class="mp-tabs__btn is-active" data-tab-btn="p1">Unleash the Power</button>
            <button class="mp-tabs__btn" data-tab-btn="p2">Precision Handling</button>
            <button class="mp-tabs__btn" data-tab-btn="p3">Engineering Marvel</button>
          </div>
          <div class="mp-tabs__root" data-tab-root>

            <div class="mp-feature is-active" data-tab-panel="p1">
              <div class="mp-feature__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/perf-1.jpg" alt="EMPOW R 2.0L GDI Turbo engine" /></div>
              <div class="mp-feature__body">
                <h3 class="mp-feature__title">Unleash the Power</h3>
                <p>Experience the thrill of the high-performance EMPOW R engine.</p>
                <ul class="mp-feature__list">
                  <li><strong>Next-Generation 2.0L GDI Turbo Engine:</strong> Delivers high power, a top speed of up to 250 km/h, fuel efficiency, and trusted reliability.</li>
                  <li><strong>8-Speed Aisin Automatic Transmission.</strong></li>
                  <li><strong>0–100 km/h Acceleration in 5.70 Seconds.</strong></li>
                  <li><strong>Four Driving Modes:</strong> Track, Sport, Comfort, and Eco.</li>
                  <li><strong>Idle Stop &amp; Go (ISG) &amp; Electronic Parking Brake (EPB) with Auto Hold:</strong> Engine auto shut-off at full stop for enhanced fuel efficiency.</li>
                  <li><strong>Comfort-Tuned Suspension &amp; Advanced Airbag System:</strong> Front MacPherson, rear multi-link beam; dual front, front side and side-curtain airbags.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mp-feature" data-tab-panel="p2">
              <div class="mp-feature__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/perf-2.jpg" alt="EMPOW R precision handling" /></div>
              <div class="mp-feature__body">
                <h3 class="mp-feature__title">Precision Handling</h3>
                <p>Agile and dynamic handling for maximum control on the road.</p>
                <ul class="mp-feature__list">
                  <li><strong>Electronic Stability Program (ESP):</strong> Automatically helps stabilise the vehicle at the first sign of lost control.</li>
                  <li><strong>Hydraulic Brake Assistant (HBA):</strong> Boosts brake-pedal pressure and feel for stronger stopping power.</li>
                  <li><strong>Hill-start Hold Control (HHC):</strong> Stops the vehicle rolling backwards when setting off uphill.</li>
                  <li><strong>Electronic Brakeforce Distribution (EBD):</strong> Minimises stopping distance and stabilises braking under load.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mp-feature" data-tab-panel="p3">
              <div class="mp-feature__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/perf-3.jpg" alt="EMPOW R engineering and efficiency" /></div>
              <div class="mp-feature__body">
                <h3 class="mp-feature__title">Engineering Marvel</h3>
                <p>Innovative technologies and superior craftsmanship for unmatched performance and efficiency.</p>
                <ul class="mp-feature__list">
                  <li><strong>Electric Power Steering (EPS):</strong> A key technology for highly automated driving.</li>
                  <li><strong>Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS):</strong> Real-time tyre-pressure information to the driver.</li>
                  <li><strong>Anti-lock Braking System (ABS):</strong> Prevents wheel lock under heavy braking so you keep steering.</li>
                  <li><strong>Max. Torque:</strong> 400 N·m.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ SAFETY ============ -->
    <section class="mp-section mp-section--grey" id="safety">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="mp-head mp-head--left">
          <h2 class="mp-head__title">Safety and Security Features</h2>
          <p class="mp-head__sub">Your Safety Is Our Priority</p>
          <p class="mp-head__body">Equipped with 10 airbags, rear door child safety locks, and ISOFix child seat anchors.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="mp-stoggles">
          <article class="mp-stoggle is-open">
            <button class="mp-stoggle__head" type="button" aria-expanded="true"><span>Comprehensive Protection</span><i class="mp-stoggle__icon"></i></button>
            <div class="mp-stoggle__body">
              <div class="mp-stoggle__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/safe-1.jpg" alt="Comprehensive Protection" loading="lazy" /></div>
              <h3 class="mp-stoggle__strap">Comprehensive Protection</h3>
              <p class="mp-stoggle__content">Integrated Cruise Assist (ICA) and Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC).</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="mp-stoggle">
            <button class="mp-stoggle__head" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><span>Safe Body Design</span><i class="mp-stoggle__icon"></i></button>
            <div class="mp-stoggle__body">
              <div class="mp-stoggle__media"><img src="/assets/img/empow-sport/safe-2.jpg" alt="Safe body design" loading="lazy" /></div>
              <h3 class="mp-stoggle__strap">Safe Body Design</h3>
              <p class="mp-stoggle__content">High strength safety body design.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="mp-stoggle">
